This package contains the accompanying material for "HardScope: Hardware-assisted
Run-time Scope Enforcement" including additional documents on the instruction set
extension and ProFTPd DOP-attack, test program used for evaluation, and patches
and installation instructions for RISC-V toolchain including RISC-V simulator
and build tools.

Contents of sub-directories:
- docs: additional documents
- dopserv: evaluation code and instructions for building and running it
- toolchain: RISC-V toolchain installation instructions and patches
